main event: A civilian couple observed an unidentified elliptical aircraft over Lake Michigan near Wilmette, Illinois on 31 May 1950.
interesting points: The aircraft was observed while the couple was seated in their parked car,The object was estimated to be 50 to 100 feet in diameter,It changed course and traveled south at a tremendous speed,The object had a slight pinkish hue during the sighting,The sighting lasted for about 10 seconds.
